Leftistpol reading list:
/lit/ general for leftists:

The first thing I am going to recommend is going to be Das Kapital itself.
Yeah it's dense as fuck, but, don't be a bitch. Get it out of the way and you will feel better and Understand a shitload more about the world and the economy. 

https://www.marxists.org/archive/marx/works/1867-c1/

De-spook yourself with this pivotal piece of literature so that you may understand your justifications for the desire to overthrow the ruling class as one of self interest and, as such, will be philosophically grounded on a solid foundation.

https://theanarchistlibrary.org/library/max-stirner-the-ego-and-his-own

Third I will recommend is "First as a tragedy then as a farce" by Slavoj Zizek.
This book will help expose you to ideology; help you understand what it is and how it functions and how to combat  it. (ultimately leading to a greater more refined understanding of the truth.)

https://selforganizedseminar.files.wordpress.com/2011/07/zizek_-tragedy_farce.pdf

...and last but not least: Mutual aid a factor in evolution.
Mutual aid a factor in evolution combats the long held and misunderstood notion of social Darwinism and pushes the reader to understand evolution from a perspective of cooperation and in ways he may not have thought of before in order to expose the read to a side of evolution which often gets glossed over when discussing it.

https://theanarchistlibrary.org/library/petr-kropotkin-mutual-aid-a-factor-of-evolution

These are my four top recommend staples for anyone curious about or getting into leftist /lit/

Other recommend reads: 
https://theanarchistlibrary.org/library/petr-kropotkin-the-conquest-of-bread

https://theanarchistlibrary.org/library/the-anarchist-faq-editorial-collective-an-anarchist-faq-15-17

https://www.marxists.org/archive/marx/works/1847/wage-labour/

https://theanarchistlibrary.org/library/emma-goldman-anarchism-and-other-essays

https://theanarchistlibrary.org/library/brian-a-dominick-animal-liberation-and-social-revolution

https://theanarchistlibrary.org/library/subversive-energy-beyond-animal-liberation

https://theanarchistlibrary.org/library/bob-black-the-abolition-of-work

Please feel more than welcome to share!

Enjoy!
